OL,6,FAnd he said the department's permanent
OL,7,Fsecretary advised the minister not to
OL,8,Fsack him. He said he was speaking out
OL,9,Fbecause his sacking had damaged his
OL,10,Freputation.
OL,12,F"I'm sitting here now, because in the
OL,13,Fend, all any of us have is our
OL,14,Freputation."
