OL,3,CHealth minister needed 'a scapegoat,'
OL,4,Csays sacked health trust chair
OL,6,F"It's interesting because one of the
OL,7,Ffirst things that the minister said in
OL,8,Fthe health committee when the issue
OL,9,Faround cardiac surgery first broke was
OL,10,Fthat he wanted to look Ciaran Mulgrew
OL,11,Fin the eye and ask him about these
OL,12,Fthings and tell him that they were
OL,13,Funacceptable.
OL,15,F"Yet when he was sacking me, he didn't
OL,16,Fturn his camera on, so I don't know if
OL,17,Fhe was in the room on his own or
OL,18,Fwhether there were other people with
OL,19,Fhim."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
