OL,3,CHealth minister needed 'a scapegoat,'
OL,4,Csays sacked health trust chair
OL,6,FIn recent weeks, there have been a
OL,7,Fnumber of concerns raised about the
OL,8,Fculture within the Belfast Trust,
OL,9,Fincluding allegations of bullying and
OL,10,Fmismanagement by senior staff.
OL,12,FThese revelations culminated in Mr
OL,13,FMulgrew's dismissal as the Department
OL,14,Fof Health said a "fresh start is
OL,15,Frequired".
OL,17,FHowever, the former chair of the Trust
OL,18,Fhas defended his record at the
OL,19,Forganisation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
