OL,3,CHealth minister needed 'a scapegoat,'
OL,4,Csays sacked health trust chair
OL,6,F"Now what kind of governance is that
OL,7,Fwhere the minister determines that I
OL,8,Fam not the right person to lead the
OL,9,Ftrust but then asks me to interview
OL,10,Fand appoint the chief executive. So I
OL,11,Fthink that has to call into account
OL,12,Fthe minister's judgment."
OL,14,FIn a statement, the Health Minister
OL,15,Fsaid: "I have no wish to engage in a
OL,16,Fwar of words with Mr Mulgrew and I
OL,17,Fwish him well for the future. I have
OL,18,Fpublicly thanked him for his
OL,19,Fcontribution to the Trust and wider
OL,20,FHealth and Social Care system.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
