OL,3,CHealth minister needed 'a scapegoat,'
OL,4,Csays sacked health trust chair
OL,6,F"However, he has made a number of
OL,7,Fassertions to UTV which I do not
OL,8,Frecognise as fact. Belfast Trust is
OL,9,Four largest Trust in NI and is one of
OL,10,Fthe largest of its kind anywhere in
OL,11,Fthe UK. It is a complex and
OL,12,Fchallenging organisation to manage. As
OL,13,FHealth Minister, I need to have
OL,14,Fconfidence in those in charge of the
OL,15,Forganisation.
OL,17,F"It is also the case that events can
OL,18,Fconspire against individuals, however
OL,19,Fwell-intentioned, and can make their
OL,20,Fposition untenable.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
