OL,3,CHealth minister needed 'a scapegoat,'
OL,4,Csays sacked health trust chair
OL,6,F"After serious consideration,
OL,7,Freflecting on the seriousness of
OL,8,Fcurrent problems, I reached the
OL,9,Fconclusion that a new start is needed
OL,10,Fat the Trust with a new chair as well
OL,11,Fas the new chief executive. I believe
OL,12,Fthat is in the best interests of the
OL,13,Forganisation, its staff and all those
OL,14,Fwho rely on its services."
